Following is the code for a querybot that answers most frequently answered questions for Microsoft Azure training.
  it can answer the provided preset questions in a formal manner with details about its confidence levels and source.
you can also add multiple PDFs or URLs to the provided code.
On starting the required setting this code can also act as a chit chat bot. It provides answers for the questions possible.
to the questions it cannot provide answers to, it shows "Sorry, I don't understand this!"

!!GOOD LUCK WORKING WITH THE CHATBOT!!
